Build using:
	python setup.py build_ext


Internal data handling:
        Coordinates are ordered as (x, y) in 2D and (x, y, z) in 3D.
        Those Coordinates are mapped to an internal Morton-ordering of
        ... y2    y1    y0               in 2D
               x2    x1    x0
        ... z2       z1       z0         in 3D
               y2       y1       y0
                  x2       x1       x0


Sample usage:
	$ python
	>>> import morton
	>>> morton.xy2d(3, 2)
	13
	>>> morton.d2xy(13)
	(3, 2)
	>>> morton.d2xyz(13)
	(3, 0, 1)
	>>> morton.xyz2d(3, 0, 1)
	13
